Title: F. Emasculata
Plot: When a plague-like illness kills ten men inside a maximum security prison, Scully tries to get into the quarantine site and discover the cause and origin of the contagion, while Mulder and a group of US Marshals track two escapees who may be infected.
GuestStars: Charles Martin Smith, Dean Norris, John Pyper-Ferguson, John Tench, Morris Panych, Lynda Boyd, Alvin Sanders, Kim Kondrashoff, Chilton Crane, Bill Rowat, Jude Zachary, Angelo Vacco, Jenny-Lynn Hutcheson
